{"tid":1615401,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[同我推上熱門]林鄭今晚7點會係會展出現！仲有李家超葉劉聶德權羅范中聯辦等!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T11:29:22.000Z","uid":30688,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e169b3163965553571df435799964e8d0652cddc","tid":1615401,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"轉自TG<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可靠消息，<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭</span>將會係今日10月3日<span style=\"color: gold;\">夜晚7點灣仔會展</span>參加頒獎禮！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">收到風除左林鄭，仲有<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">李家超<br />\n葉劉<br />\n聶德權<br />\n羅范<br />\n李國章<br />\n中聯辦要員</span><br />\n...等等...不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n粒粒巨星，唔係唔去支持下呱　<br />\n<br />\n好想瘋狂同Carrie 姐姐對話呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係大家千其唔好圍呀，因間搞到班高官無得返屋企點算？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f767a89a89f70e712d0c26cde9f4b6497611b9dc","tid":1615401,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"befd30d9fecf823f8b087d6549593e1d6b29dc2e","tid":1615401,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bca712e270a9c0ed02fa8667a27fb93ec07374de","tid":1615401,"uid":223226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T05:40:08.000Z","msg":"[戰書] 致香港人：呢個係我俾大家嘅最後限期<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/egQcCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/egQcCS</a><br />\n<br />\n二百萬聯合陣線（公海）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data